rooms.name: Forgotten Chamber
rooms.description: You step into the Forgotten Chamber, a modest-sized room where dust hangs in the stale air and cracked flagstones seem to remember a quiet bustle now gone. Sparse furnishings—a splintered chair, a rust-rimmed basin, and a low chest—throw long, uncertain shadows by a single guttering torch, and each echoing footfall stirs a hush of memory that wants to be left undisturbed.

rooms.name: Silent Library
rooms.description: You step into the Silent Library, where vaulted stone arches swallow sound and your footsteps return to you as distant, reluctant echoes. Shelves stand like sentinels across the vast, dust-scented hall, broken only by a lone iron lectern and a worn chair; thin shafts of cold light pick out leather spines and motes that drift as if time itself reads on in whispers.

rooms.name: Noble's Bedroom
rooms.description: You cross the threshold into the Noble's Bedroom, a vast chamber where vaulted stone swallows sound and the emptiness reads like deliberate restraint. A single canopied bed of faded velvet, an iron chest, and a narrow barred window casting a knife of cold light stand as scant honors; dust, old perfume, and the whisper of distant water linger in the chill.

rooms.name: Dark Crypt
rooms.description: You step into the Dark Crypt and the vast vault swallows your footsteps, a high-arched ceiling vanishing into a pool of unlit shadow as your breath rings against bare stone. Sparse furnishings — a single cracked sarcophagus, a rusted brazier of cold ash, and a low table strewn with brittle bone — punctuate the hollow hush, each object a silent marker where drafts and memory conspire to shape the dark.

rooms.name: Cursed Throne Room
rooms.description: You cross the threshold into the Cursed Throne Room, a cavernous hall where every footstep is swallowed by an oppressive hush and a single blackened dais bears a throne of twisted iron and dried blood. Sparsely furnished with torn banners, a toppled candlestick, and a cracked altar, the air tastes of rust and old grief while shadows pool around the throne like patient, watchful things that whisper names you almost remember.

rooms.name: Master Bedroom
rooms.description: You step into the Master Bedroom, a modest, low-ceilinged chamber where cold stone exhales the faint smell of mildew and old smoke. A single iron bed with a lumpy mattress and a threadbare blanket crouches beneath a shuttered slit of a window, while a small chest and a splintered chair stand like mute witnesses in the dim puddle of a dying candle. Every breath tastes of dust and damp, and the slow, patient drip from the corridor punctuates the hush like a watchman's heartbeat.

m_8d8f428e.name: Dark Cultist
m_8d8f428e.description: A hooded figure devoted to dark powers, wielding forbidden magic.
